# Sample .sneakpackignore for a field-research tree.
# Copy to the root of your source directory as ".sneakpackignore".
# The file itself is tracked and synced, so both sides agree on the rules.

# scratch and editor files, wherever they appear
*.tmp
*.swp

# whole directories that never need to travel (note the trailing slash)
cache/
raw-video/

# anchored: only the top-level scratch dir, not every "scratch" below
/scratch/

# equipment logs are huge and local...
sensors/**/*.log
# ...except the calibration log, which the base station needs
!calibration.log
